{
  "texts": [
    "Meanwhile, raw PDF data contain many extra spaces between words, inconsistent parentheses, and inconsistent sentence segmentation [72].",
    "Punctuation like (+, -, /, *, (,), &,%,.,), ÷, ×,],], }, {, <, >, \\, -, @, #) also need to be cleaned from the corpus [76].",
    "These various noises must be cleaned to produce a clean corpus ready to be annotated.",
    "This cleaning step is also useful for reducing the dimensions of the corpus.Sentence segmentation is a preprocessing stage that is useful for parsing the text in the document into sentences.",
    "One segment contains one sentence."
  ]
}